{"tid":1736790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無哂啲行動po 大家係咪已經想放棄 覺得好攰？","createTime":"2019-11-18T19:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T22:05:15.000Z","uid":266636,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a925416df4675358e85df03066b1b997662a7b1","tid":1736790,"uid":266636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:59:54.000Z","msg":"今日的確發生咗好多事 <br />\nPoly 嘅手足仲有好多人被困<br />\n係佐敦同尖沙咀亦有多手足想救人<br />\n不幸俾狗咬  又少咗好多勇武 少咗好多手足<br />\n<br />\n今日我哋的確係輸得好慘 <br />\n不過係咪咁就要絕望呢？<br />\n見lihkg 成個熱門都係啲負能量po<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我想講仲有班手足係poly 入面等我哋救 佢哋仲未投降 我哋有乜資格放棄</span><br />\n如果我哋係出面都咁想放棄 咁佢哋點算<br />\n<br />\n快啲諗吓聽日嘅行動po 仲好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要出 要相信我哋一定贏到 好無？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0a3c689d44a2c463e74b6d72ddfc84a31150f929","tid":1736790,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:01:07.000Z","msg":"瞓唔着嘅，不如入嚟睇下<br />\n<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65bb01aba56d0a77198720ef4487a578a26c9a03","tid":1736790,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:23:29.000Z","msg":"新時代誕生"},{"pid":"87b652f413e7980c1cfd77d95db43874b363e292","tid":1736790,"uid":62523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:24:21.000Z","msg":"哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2568e4721dc8b76b02a34f8eac3f2cba50c9516","tid":1736790,"uid":171804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e958b0e584a911ec1bb8467429c61f13ea3ce90f","tid":1736790,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T21:59:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt l